Describe things using all of a persons senses. Smell can be a great way to bring players into a new location. Describe what they hear, see, smell, and possibly feel if like if it's breezy or hot or cold.

Try having players strong in certain attributes gain passive insight into npcs or other things. Not sure how exactly I want to handle it but at the very least it can breath some life into NPCs the players encounter if they're learning some innate trait about that character.
